        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<p>A goo grenade is a flask filled with a fast-growing, short-lived alchemical ooze. When you hit a creature with a goo grenade, that creature takes 3d4 acid damage, 3 persistent acid damage, and 3 acid splash damage, and a -10 circumstance penalty to its Speeds from the clinging goo. You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The target can end any penalties, conditions, and persistent damage caused by the bomb by Escaping (DC 26) or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to pry themselves free of the ooze. These Interact actions don't have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.Effect: Goo Grenade]</p>"
